<div class="collection-page" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/CollectionPage">
  <div class="collection-banner">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Functional Mushroom Seltzers · No Alcohol · No Caffeine</div>
    <h1 itemprop="name">{{ collection.title }}</h1>
    {%- if collection.description != blank -%}
      <p itemprop="description">{{ collection.description }}</p>
    {%- else -%}
      <p>Shop Happie Fungi Fusion functional mushroom seltzers — 900mg Lion's Mane, 700mg Cordyceps &amp; 400mg Reishi per can. The best alcohol-free, caffeine-free adaptogenic drink. Free shipping on orders over $35.</p>
    {%- endif -%}
    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-top:16px;">
      <span style="background:rgba(82,183,136,0.12);color:var(--green);border-radius:50px;padding:6px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;">🍄 2,000mg Per Can</span>
      <span style="background:rgba(82,183,136,0.12);color:var(--green);border-radius:50px;padding:6px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;">✅ 0% Alcohol</span>
      <span style="background:rgba(82,183,136,0.12);color:var(--green);border-radius:50px;padding:6px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;">⚡ 0mg Caffeine</span>
      <span style="background:rgba(82,183,136,0.12);color:var(--green);border-radius:50px;padding:6px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;">🧪 Third-Party Lab Tested</span>
      <span style="background:rgba(82,183,136,0.12);color:var(--green);border-radius:50px;padding:6px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;">🌿 Vegan &amp; Non-GMO</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="products-grid">
      {% for product in collection.products %}
        {% render 'product-card', product: product %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SEO content block — premium redesign -->
  <div class="coll-seo-section">
    <div class="coll-seo-inner">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="coll-seo-header">
        <div class="coll-seo-eyebrow">Why We're Different</div>
        <h2 class="coll-seo-title">Why Happie Fungi Fusion is the best<br>functional mushroom drink</h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Two-col: text + mushroom cards -->
      <div class="coll-seo-grid">
        <div class="coll-seo-text">
          <p>Most functional mushroom supplements bury ineffective doses in capsules made from mycelium grown on grain — more grain starch than active compounds. Happie Fungi Fusion is different: we use only <strong>fruiting body extracts</strong>, dual-extracted (hot water + ethanol) for the full spectrum of beta-glucans and triterpenes.</p>
          <p>Each 12oz can delivers a complete adaptogenic stack — totaling <strong>2,000mg of active mushroom extract</strong>. Zero alcohol. Zero caffeine. ~40 calories. Available in <a href="/products/watermelon-fungi-powered-seltzer">Watermelon</a>, <a href="/products/mango-mimosa-fungi-powered-seltzer">Mango Mimosa</a>, <a href="/products/blue-razzberry-fungi-powered-seltzer">Blue Razzberry</a>, and a <a href="/products/happie-fungi-fusion-mushroom-drink-variety-pack">12-can Variety Pack</a>.</p>
          <!-- Link pills -->
          <div class="coll-seo-links">
            <a href="/pages/the-science" class="coll-seo-link">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 3h6l1 4H8L9 3z"/><path d="M8 7v10a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h6a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V7"/><path d="M12 11v3M11 13h2"/></svg>
              The Science of Dual Extraction
            </a>
            <a href="/pages/mushrooms" class="coll-seo-link">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12s4.5 10 10 10 10-4.5 10-10S17.5 2 12 2"/><path d="M8.56 2.75c4.37 6.03 6.02 9.42 8.03 17.72M10.48 21.24c1.94-9.38 5.15-13.84 8.1-18.68"/></svg>
              About the Mushrooms
            </a>
            <a href="/pages/faq" class="coll-seo-link">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
              FAQ
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mushroom stat cards -->
        <div class="coll-seo-cards">
          <div class="coll-mush-card coll-mush-lion">
            <div class="coll-mush-dose">900mg</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-name">Lion's Mane</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-benefit">Focus &amp; Cognition</div>
            <p class="coll-mush-desc">Stimulates Nerve Growth Factor (NGF) for sharper focus and mental clarity. Dual-extracted fruiting body.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="coll-mush-card coll-mush-cord">
            <div class="coll-mush-dose">700mg</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-name">Cordyceps</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-benefit">Natural Energy</div>
            <p class="coll-mush-desc">Supports ATP production for sustained energy — no caffeine, no crash. Pure cellular fuel.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="coll-mush-card coll-mush-rei">
            <div class="coll-mush-dose">400mg</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-name">Reishi</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-benefit">Calm &amp; Stress</div>
            <p class="coll-mush-desc">The queen of mushrooms. Triterpenes support the body's stress response for deep calm without sedation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
  .coll-seo-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, var(--cream, #F5F0E8) 100%);
    padding: 80px 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .coll-seo-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .coll-seo-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .coll-seo-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--green, #52B788);
    background: rgba(82,183,136,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(82,183,136,0.2);
    padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .coll-seo-title {
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 38px);
    font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .coll-seo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .coll-seo-text p {
    font-size: 15px; color: #4A4A4A;
    line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .coll-seo-text p:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .coll-seo-text strong { color: #1A1A1A; }
  .coll-seo-text a {
    color: var(--green, #52B788);
    font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(82,183,136,0.3);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .coll-seo-text a:hover { border-color: var(--green, #52B788); }

  .coll-seo-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .coll-seo-link {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(82,183,136,0.25);
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F);
    text-decoration: none !important;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgba(82,183,136,0.25) !important;
    width: fit-content;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .coll-seo-link:hover {
    background: var(--green, #52B788);
    border-color: var(--green, #52B788) !important;
    color: #fff;
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }
  .coll-seo-link svg { flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* Mushroom cards */
  .coll-seo-cards { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }

  .coll-mush-card {
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px 26px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .coll-mush-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .coll-mush-lion {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EBF8F0, #D4EDDE);
    border-color: rgba(82,183,136,0.2);
  }
  .coll-mush-cord {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF8ED, #FDECD0);
    border-color: rgba(245,166,35,0.2);
  }
  .coll-mush-rei {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F0EEF8, #E2DEEF);
    border-color: rgba(98,96,174,0.2);
  }

  .coll-mush-dose {
    font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .coll-mush-lion .coll-mush-dose { color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F); }
  .coll-mush-cord .coll-mush-dose { color: #B45309; }
  .coll-mush-rei .coll-mush-dose { color: #4C3B9A; }

  .coll-mush-name {
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .coll-mush-lion .coll-mush-name { color: var(--green, #52B788); }
  .coll-mush-cord .coll-mush-name { color: #D97706; }
  .coll-mush-rei .coll-mush-name { color: #6260AE; }

  .coll-mush-benefit {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .coll-mush-lion .coll-mush-benefit { background: rgba(82,183,136,0.15); color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F); }
  .coll-mush-cord .coll-mush-benefit { background: rgba(245,166,35,0.15); color: #92400E; }
  .coll-mush-rei .coll-mush-benefit { background: rgba(98,96,174,0.15); color: #3730A3; }

  .coll-mush-desc {
    font-size: 13px; color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .coll-seo-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .coll-seo-section { padding: 60px 20px; }
    .coll-seo-title br { display: none; }
  }
  </style>
</div>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "ItemList",
  "name": "Happie Fungi Fusion Functional Mushroom Seltzers",
  "description": "Functional mushroom seltzers with 900mg Lion's Mane, 700mg Cordyceps, and 400mg Reishi per can. Zero alcohol, zero caffeine.",
  "itemListElement": [
    {% for product in collection.products %}
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": {{ forloop.index }},
      "name": {{ product.title | json }},
      "url": "https://happiefusion.com/products/{{ product.handle }}",
      "image": "https:{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 }}",
      "description": {{ product.description | strip_html | truncate: 200 | json }}
    }{% unless forloop.last %},{% endunless %}
    {% endfor %}
  ]
}
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Main Collection",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
